'''Marc Twagirumukiza''' (wavutse 1973, avukira mu [[Rwanda]] ) ni umuganga ukorera mububiligi akaba n'umushakashatsi mukuru w’ubuvuzi mu bijyanye nama farumasi ,cardiovascular and hypertension research, epidemiology, electronic health records, real world data / real world evidence and semantic web technology in health sciences. . Ni umuyobozi wa World Wide Web Consortium Healthcare Schema Vocabulary Community Group. <ref name="ScheMed">[https://www.w3.org/community/schemed W3C Healthcare Schema Vocabulary Community Group]</ref>

== Uburezi ==
Twagirumukiza ni umuganga kandi yarangije impamyabumenyi ya PhD muri farumasi y’ubuvuzi yakuye muri kaminuza ya Ghent, mu [[Ububiligi|Bubiligi]] mu 2010.

== amasomo ==
Yabaye umuganga mu bitaro bya kaminuza y'u Rwanda i [[Butare]], Intara y’Amajyepfo [[Rwanda|y’Urwanda]] akaba n'umwarimu mu cyahoze ari ishami ry’ubuvuzi muri [[kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda]] kuri ubu izwi ku izina rya College of Medicine and Science Science muri [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|kaminuza yu Rwanda]] kuva 2001 kugeza 2005. Yari kandi umwarimu mu mashuri abiri y’ubuvuzi yo muri Afurika (u Rwanda, u [[Uburundi|Burundi]], [[Mozambike]], na [[Kenya]] na yandi) kuva 2001 kugeza 2013. Kuri ubu akora nka mwarimu wubuvuzi na farumasi  muri kaminuza ya Ghent kandi akora mubushakashatsi butandukanye bwubuvuzi nubuzima: Clinical Pharmacology na Clinical Trials, <ref name="pmid25369200">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4219663</ref> ubuzima rusange, <ref name="pmid21144194">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2991737</ref> ubushakashatsi rusange , <ref name="pmid19861610">https://doi.org/10.4269%2Fajtmh.2009.09-0109</ref> nubushakashatsi bwamavuriro . <ref name="pmid17266564">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Current_HIV_Research</ref> <ref name="atmph2008_1">https://doi.org/10.4103%2F1755-6783.43071</ref>  ubushakashatsi bwumutima nimiyoboro y'amaraso (cyane cyane umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso hamwe no gukomera kwa arterial muri Afurika yo munsi y'Ubutayu bwa Sahara ), kubona imiti (kuboneka, gutera inkunga no gutanga amasoko, ibiciro kandi bihendutse, amabwiriza na politiki) mubihugu byinjiza amafaranga make., <ref name="access-to-medicines">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Campaign_for_Access_to_Essential_Medicines</ref> <ref name="pmid20070634">https://doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.1365-3156.2009.02453.x</ref> n'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze . <ref name="pmid20336148">https://doi.org/10.1038%2Fjhh.2010.32</ref>

== Ibikorwa bya web semantique hamwe nakazi ==


Yagize uruhare mu myubakire yamakuru rusange asanzwe <ref name="CIMv2">[http://www.srdc.com.tr/projects/salus/blog/?p=342 Common Information Model of SALUS]</ref> yakoreshejwe na semantique layer mumushinga SALUS. <ref name="salus">[http://www.salusproject.eu SALUS EU FP7 Project]</ref> SALUS isobanura "Urwego ruringaniza, rushingiye ku mikoranire ishingiye ku bushakashatsi burambye bwo Kwiga ku Isoko". Intego yacyo kwari ugutanga imyirondoro yimikorere ituma habaho guhanahana amakuru yubuzima bwa elegitoronike, ibisubizo bisobanutse bifasha gusobanura neza inyandiko zahinduwe, umutekano n’ubuzima bwite byerekana ko inyandiko z’ubuzima bwa elegitoronike zisaranganywa mu buryo bw’imyitwarire n’umutekano, urwego rushya. kubintu byafunguye-byigihe gito byavumbuwe kubushakashatsi bwumutekano hejuru ya sisitemu no gushyira mubikorwa byinshi bishobora gukoreshwa bifasha gukoresha kabiri inyandiko zubuzima bwa elegitoronike hamwe namakuru yukuri kwisi / ibimenyetso bifatika kwisi kubushakashatsi bwumutekano nyuma yisoko. Twagirumukiza nuwashinze  World Wide Web Consortium Healthcare Schema Vocabulary Community Group. <ref name="ScheMed">[https://www.w3.org/community/schemed W3C Healthcare Schema Vocabulary Community Group]</ref>

== Imiyoboro ==
Twagirumukiza ni umunyamuryango wa societe siyanse harimo na komite ishinzwe umuvuduko ukabije w’amaraso mu bubiligi, <ref name="bhc">http://www.belhypcom.be/</ref> n'abandi.  Ku mugabane wa Afurika azwiho no mu bikorwa bya siyanse harimo no mu bindi bihugu bigize Pan-African Society of Cardiology (PASCAR), <ref name="pascar">http://www.pascar.org/</ref> Task Force ya Hypertension. PASCAR ni ishyirahamwe ryabaganga baturutse muri [[Afurika|Afrika yose]] igira uruhare mukurinda no kuvura indwara zifata umutima nimiyoboro yimitsi kandi ihangayikishijwe no kudatera imbere mugupima no kuvura neza indwara zifata umutima nimiyoboro muri Afrika.Twagirumukiza kandi yari umwe mu bahanga batangije gahunda y’umuryango nyafurika wa Hypertension (AfSoH), <ref name="societies1">http://www.afsoh.com/</ref> ihuriro ry’inzobere mu buzima n’abashakashatsi bakora mu bijyanye na hypertension arterial ku [[Afurika|mugabane wa Afurika]] .

